012)51:4%3C387::AID-CCD3%3E3.0.CO;2-B">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/11108666/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Iatrogenic+coronary+artery+dissections+extending+into+and+involving+the+aortic+root&amp;author=DW+Dunning&amp;author=JK+Kahn&amp;author=ET+Hawkins&amp;author=WW+O%E2%80%99Neill&amp;publication_year=2000&amp;journal=Catheter+Cardiovasc+Interv&amp;pages=387-393&amp;doi=10.1002%2F1522-726X%28200012%2951%3A4%253C387%3A%3AAID-CCD3%253E3.0.CO%3B2-B&amp;pmid=11108666">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">8.</div><div id="r8" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Steffenino G, Meier B, Finci L, et al. Acute complications of elective coronary angioplasty: a review of 500 consecutive procedures. <em>Br Heart J</em> 1988;59(2):151–158.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1136/hrt.59.2.151">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/2963656/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Acute+complications+of+elective+coronary+angioplasty%3A+a+review+of+500+consecutive+procedures&amp;author=G+Steffenino&amp;author=B+Meier&amp;author=L+Finci&amp;publication_year=1988&amp;journal=Br+Heart+J&amp;pages=151-158&amp;doi=10.1136%2Fhrt.59.2.151&amp;pmid=2963656">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">9.</div><div id="r9" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Kimmel SE, Berlin JA, Hennessy S, Strom BL, Krone RJ, Laskey WK. Risk of major complications from coronary angioplasty performed immediately after diagnostic coronary angiography: results from the Registry of the Society 